text: 10 is a 1979 American romantic comedy movie directed by Blake Edwards and starring Dudley Moore, Julie Andrews, Bo Derek, Robert Webber, Dee Wallace and Brian Dennehy. It was distributed by Warner Bros. and was nominated for 2 Academy Awards in 1980. ==Other websites== * * Category:1979 romantic comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by Blake Edwards Category:1970s English-language movies Category:American sex comedy movies Category:Midlife crisis movies
